schemas.name: queries.graphql

merged.mergedContent:
# https://github.com/cryptoPickle/GraphQL-Auth-Service/blob/11b3925fd33ad01040be15ebbbdf281be75b6e03/dist/queries.graphql:
type Query {
  getUserById(id: ID!) : User!
  getTokens: Token!
  getProfile: User!
}
# https://github.com/cryptoPickle/GraphQL-Auth-Service/blob/ffd2beb4b467058f21c3efdb2dbfe87d51b4174c/dist/user.schema.graphql:
enum Gender {
  male
  female
  other
}

type User {
  id: ID!
  email: String!
  password: String
  name: String!
  surname: String!
  age: Int
  birthday: String
  gender: Gender
  google_profile_id: String
  google_verified: Boolean
  facebook_profile_id: String
  facebook_verified: Boolean
  isCompleted: Boolean
  email_verified: Boolean
  isFrozen: Boolean
  created_at: String
  updated_at: String
  delete_at: String
}


# https://github.com/cryptoPickle/GraphQL-Auth-Service/blob/11b3925fd33ad01040be15ebbbdf281be75b6e03/dist/token.schema.graphql:
type Token {
  id: ID!
  user_id: ID!
  google_access_token: String
  facebook_access_token: String
  jwt_refresh_token: String
  jwt_access_token: String
  created_at: String
  updated_at: String
}
